{"article_id":"s6C4nMZrQIiFDB4V","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"LONDON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Donald Trump lashed out at French President Emmanuel Macron on Tuesday","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"as the two leaders met for talks on the sidelines of NATO meetings in Britain 's capital .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"Trump is in London for a gathering","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"connected to the military alliance 's 70th anniversary amid quarrels over defense spending , fights about trade and climate policy , rifts over Turkey 's actions in Syria , and Iran .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"The official program starts Wednesday .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"But ahead of that , Trump said Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that recent comments from Macron","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"that NATO is experiencing `` brain death ''","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"were `` very nasty '' and `` very insulting '' to the alliance 's other 28 members .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"`` Nobody needs NATO more than France , ''","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"`` It 's a very dangerous statement for them to make , ''","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Trump also said","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"as his NATO visit now risks being overshadowed by his meeting with Macron .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"`` Macron is seizing ( the ) moment ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"seeking to be disruptive in his own way ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"and so we will see how that works , ''","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"said Heather Conley , a foreign affairs expert at the Center for Strategic and International Studies , a Washington think tank .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"NATO comes to London :","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"Cracks in alliance 's armor begin to show","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"Among Macron 's disruptions :","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"continuing to argue for the relevance of the Iran nuclear deal","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"from which Trump has withdrawn ;","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"announcing at the end of August","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"that Europe needed to seek a greater accommodation with Russia and China ;","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"and his `` brain death '' comments in an interview in The Economist and a reference , in part , to NATO member Turkey 's incursion into Kurdish-held Syria","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"to root out fighters","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"it considers terrorists","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"but who had also been assisting U.S.-led forces","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"battling the Islamic State group .","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"Macron has also long argued","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"that Trump 's exit from the international climate accord was a mistake .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"And France 's president wants the military alliance ,","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"founded in 1949 as a bulwark against the then-Soviet Union ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"to pivot more toward fighting global terrorism .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"For his part , Trump has repeatedly called the alliance `` obsolete ''","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"and publicly attacked NATO members","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"for failing to meet defense spending commitments , a scenario","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"that has slowly started to be rectified","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"as more NATO allies meet required 2 % -of-GDP spending levels .","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"At last year 's NATO summit , Trump arrived late","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"and called Germany `` delinquent '' and a `` captive '' of Russia .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"`` A lot of countries have n't paid , ''","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Trump said Tuesday .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"`` You could make the case","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"that they have been delinquent for 25-30 years . ''","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"In a further ratcheting up of tensions ,","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"as Trump arrived in London on Tuesday night ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"the White House said","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"it was considering imposing tariffs on up to $ 2.4 billion worth of French goods in response to that country 's new digital services tax","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"targeting U.S. technology companies such as Amazon , Facebook and Google .","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"Macron `` wants a real strategy discussion '' about NATO ,","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"said Thomas Gomart , director of IFRI , a Paris-based international relations think tank .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"`` Not just to pretend that everything is OK . ''","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Still ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"after Trump and Macron met in person on Tuesday ,","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"the U.S. leader struck a conciliatory tone in front of media ,","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"although the chemistry between the two leaders appeared cooler","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"than it has in past encounters .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"`` We have a minor dispute .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"I think","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"we will probably be able to work it out , ''","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Macron said","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"NATO needs to refocus itself on new threats , not just money .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"Trump also raised the issue of foreign Islamic State fighters","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"captured by U.S.-led forces in Syria .","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"`` They are all under lock and key ,","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"but many are from France , many from Germany and from the U.K.","depth":15},{"id":70,"text":"Mostly from Europe .","depth":15},{"id":71,"text":"And some of the countries are agreeing .","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"I have not spoken to the president about that , ''","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"he said ,","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"turning to Macron .","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"`` Would you like some nice ISIS fighters ?","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"I can give them to you , ''","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"Trump said .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"Macron responded","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"by saying","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"that `` for me the very first objective in the region is to finish work against ( the Islamic State group ) , ''","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"a reference to Trump 's decision","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"to order U.S. troops out of Syria amid Turkey 's incursion .","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"But since Trump 's decision","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"to withdraw in October ,","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"some U.S. troops remain in the country .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"Trump has called the NATO meetings in London `` one of the most important journeys","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"that we make as president ''","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"and he kicked off a series of meetings Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"by holding closed-door talks with NATO Secretary General Jens Stoltenberg .","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"In earlier wide-ranging remarks to the press ,","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"including about Macron ' s comments on NATO ,","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"Trump said","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"`` NATO serves a great purpose . ''","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"He also criticized France for the digital services tax ,","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"that `` if anyone was going to tax American companies","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"it will be me . ''","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"Trump also addressed the prospect","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"of signing a trade deal with China ,","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"he `` likes the idea","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"of waiting until after the ( 2020 )","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"election '' for that agreement .","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"More :","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"Trump signals","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"trade deal with China could be delayed until after 2020 election","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"He described recent violent protests in Iran ,","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"in which rights group said","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"more than 200 people were killed ,","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"as a `` terrible thing . ''","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"Trump confirmed","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"that he will be meeting with U.K. Prime Minister Boris Johnson","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"but said","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"he had `` no thoughts '' about Britain 's impending general election on Dec. 12 .","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"The British press has speculated","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"that a meeting with Trump ,","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"mired","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"as he is in the impeachment inquiry back in Washington ,","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"may not be a good look for Johnson before the vote .","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"`` I do n't want to complicate it , ''","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"Trump said of Britain 's election .","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"Trump participated in a reception with Queen Elizabeth II at Buckingham Palace","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"to celebrate the military alliance .","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"He also met with Princes Charles and his wife , Camilla .","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"On North Korea ,","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"where Trump is trying to get Kim Jong Un to abandon his nuclear weapons program ,","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"Trump said","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"`` if you would ' ve listened to President Obama ,","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"we ' ll be in World War III right now . ''","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"However , talks with North Korea have stalled .","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"More :","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"North Korea warns","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"US may get nasty 'Christmas gift '","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"if nuke deal not reached by Dec. 31 deadline","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"Gulnur Aybet , a senior adviser to Turkey 's President Recep Tayyip Erdogan , said","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"her government 's decision","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"to invade northeastern Syria","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"`` was not a NATO issue . ''","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"Macron has expressed displeasure at Turkey 's failure","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"to coordinate its Syria actions with NATO , an operation","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"the rest of the alliance opposed .","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"While he wo n't be in Washington for Wednesday 's impeachment hearing","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"in which the House Judiciary Committee will unveil witnesses ,","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"the inquiry has followed Trump to London .","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"That 's largely by his own design .","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"`` Just landed in the United Kingdom ,","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"heading to London for NATO meetings tomorrow .","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"Prior to landing","depth":15},{"id":150,"text":"I read the Republicans Report on the Impeachment Hoax .","depth":15},{"id":151,"text":"Great job !","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"Radical Left has NO CASE .","depth":15},{"id":153,"text":"Read the Transcripts .","depth":16},{"id":154,"text":"Shouldn ' t even be allowed .","depth":16},{"id":155,"text":"Can we go to Supreme Court","depth":15},{"id":156,"text":"to stop ? ''","depth":15},{"id":157,"text":"the president tweeted","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"after arriving at Stansted Airport on the outskirts of London .","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"Sitting next to Stoltenberg on Tuesday ,","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"Trump said :","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"`` I did nothing wrong .","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"You don ' t censure somebody","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"when they did nothing wrong . ''","depth":11}],"rel